reviewText: I love that Bob Berg shows where he get's his materials from and how he makes each Atlatl and dart by hand!  Bob also gave detailed instruction on how to throw the dart and how to improve your accuracy.  I loved the slow-mo bits showing how the dart flies through the air, it really helps.  Check out this clip on YouTube - [...]
This video is really great. It covers everything from makeing one from scratch to casting the dart. I recomend this for anyone who wants to get started with the atlatl.
